Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.81,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord2.25\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:13.52,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:22.91,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:28.12,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.34,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.28,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:55.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:01:00.62,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:15.55,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:27.65,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this gentle light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:20.87,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}Phone Duty - Declare a State of Emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:46.43,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:49.39,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:07.74,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:13.71,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:22.55,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:26.68,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.37,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:32.66,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:34.01,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:39.99,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.98,0:23:39.99,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:45.78,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:45.78,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:52.20,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:57.75,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:02.71,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:15.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wet myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:30.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters Hotline Wiring Maintenance Confirmation for Sudden High-Priority Emergency Contact and Direction Mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:33.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a really long name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extremely important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:39.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fail, we'll all receive reprimands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:43.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the situation, a level-one security alert may be issued,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:47.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and all forces in the area placed on emergency standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:52.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's a heavy responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh- What kind of mission is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:57.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:01.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Phone duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:10.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how this is the hotline connected to headquarters in the capital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it ever rung?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:15.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It's a good thing that the phone hasn't rung,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:22.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not a good thing if it doesn't ring when necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:27.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So once every six months, they test the line to see if it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, at least remember these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:36.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters Confirmation High-Priority Emergency - wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:41.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's the Headquarters Hotline Wiring Confirmation Emergency for...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:48.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters Hotline Wiring Maintenance Confirmation for Sudden High-Priority Emergency Contact and Direction Mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Oh! Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of this mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try talking on a telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:02.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:06.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It works pretty much the same way as the intercom in the Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:08.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that the other side is far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the amazing part!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:13.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk to people so far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:13.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:20.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is a strange feeling to talk to people you can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:23.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But once you get used to it, it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:27.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The only problem is that we don't know when the call will come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:35.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll be stuck to the phone for the entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:48.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Private Kanata Sorami at Fortress 1121 of the Army of the Republic of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:55.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the call is over, we put the phone back the way it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:39.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fil- Fili-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're just so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:47.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? It hurts just to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The train might leave before we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:54.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have some documents we need to rush to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus doesn't come until next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're taking them to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep an eye on that phone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:09.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't answer, they might even think we've been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep both eyes on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:35.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single wink of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:43.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Noël around?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The hangar again, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kanata, what do you want for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:56.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I- I- I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:06.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Why do you and Kureha never let me cook whenever it's my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I cooked all the time before you two got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't taste bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:19.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't taste as bad as it looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:23.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it has a very distinct flavor! It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:29.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll put even more of my love into it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, it's Miss Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:44.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to stick to the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:47.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You've got a customer here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Guess I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:08:01.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to eat sandwiches with cutting board in them anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and drink. It's apple cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:12.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's handmade from the farm where we get our apple juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:16.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like a cousin of the calvados we make?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:17.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:22.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. She found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:30.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Two should be enough for tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:33.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a merchants' guild meeting tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:42.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We always like to provide refreshments as thanks for everything they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:43.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:50.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! They did everything they could to hide it from you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,W- Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:00.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get the chance, maybe I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:06.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Miss Naomi, how would you like to have lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:10.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You want me to attend it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:16.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, everyone wants a proper explanation from the military for the news in this week's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:17.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,News?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:21.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About how the peace treaty conferences aren't going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:28.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're squabbling over paying reparations and drawing borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:30.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows these things always take longer than they should.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:36.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more like those old geezers in the guild want to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:40.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you played the part of one of the Maidens of the Fire at the Water-Casting festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:43.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,you've been gaining quite a fanbase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:46.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bother. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:51.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there. It looks like I'll have to attend the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:55.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the Maidens of the Fortress now, heart and soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I will complete this mission by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. It's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:07.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I'd like to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:11.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry they're not new, they were mine before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these... trumpet -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful! Wonderful! Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:23.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bugling's gotten a lot better recently, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:25.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reward for practicing so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And with those, you won't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is C...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,D...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:41.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,E...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,F...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:43.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,G...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:05.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess summer's just about over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:31.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining! The laundry is getting wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The courtyard is within the field of operations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:53.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:56.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:04.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3\pos(1840,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:09.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1\pos(80,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:15.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm glad that your laundry is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So am - I mean -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you help me after you came all this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:26.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all. I'm sorry for the sudden visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:31.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I must return to Treize tomorrow, so I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though soldiers don't need goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:40.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:44.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that Seiya has been disrespectful to you in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:48.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would apologize for that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the others home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all out at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:56.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it... Rio? The black-haired one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have liked to pay my -
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:04.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this book... yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a book for the trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:12.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:18.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I'm sorry. I was just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:31.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters Hotline Wiring Maintenance Confirmation for Sudden High-Priority Emergency Contact and Direction Mission
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:39.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,you're waiting for this to ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:40.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:43.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never used one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:49.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like whether I can speak properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:51.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you like to practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:59.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So Sister Yumina is attending the guild meeting too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:04.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's gone to collect donations from the members of the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:07.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? Drink up, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:18.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll drink your stupid cider, but don't think I'll like you any more for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:30.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is. It's a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:49.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids love them, so sometimes I make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:01.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:05.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, when you pick up a phone, first you say, "Hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you use a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,H- Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing! I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:19.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can hear his voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:22.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can practice a bit with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:22.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... This is-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,H- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:35.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Private Kanata Sorami at Fortress 1121 of the Army of the Republic of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:36.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:40.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an honor to receive a call from you at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, little bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:51.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio, don't-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:08.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:32.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... Are our priest and our-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My myriad gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You only paid a visit to thank them and say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:09.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And instead, you played and made a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all clean now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:22.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:25.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But your clothes are soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I have some right over-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know what we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:42.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:44.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:46.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how dazzling you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sister Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:53.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash them before I return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can have them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:58.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too big for the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:03.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't imagine anyone who would look so dazzling in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you play with us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:10.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back again soon, okay, Seiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:14.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I- I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe when I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:30.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,May the blessings of all be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Th- Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:40.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I need to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wet myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:13.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:17.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:24.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, those old geezers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, Kana-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:29.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:33.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wet myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:43.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and do it! You'll get sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was holding it in this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:51.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She really does do whatever she's told.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:03.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:05.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:07.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:13.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, these people have horrible timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:22.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Master Sergeant Rio Kazumiya of Platoon 1121 of the Army of the Republic of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:29.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard we would be confirming your line, so I insisted -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:31.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:33.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:36.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:38.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You simply haven't forgiven me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After this long. What do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:47.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I want you to save this country! To save Helvetia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:51.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:56.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, have you been in there since morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:59.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I sleep well in the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:09.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ho- my, Kanata, what cute clothes you're wearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:13.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing in the hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:15.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata fell down. Can't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:17.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:20.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you just stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:26.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:28.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just so spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:30.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:32.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:36.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:14.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,405)\c&H020202&\bord0}One Typhoon Passes - What You Really See
